Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan Episode 1013 "The \NMan Who Loved Too Much"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,[OP]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,[ED]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,[Eyecatch]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.91,0:00:03.98,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,Smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:06.98,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,How's this coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:11.24,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:15.24,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to add \Nthe secret ingredient.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:23.20,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. Pork, potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:24.92,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Carrots, onions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.82,0:00:27.10,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Daikon radish?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.10,0:00:27.79,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Burdock root.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.78,0:00:32.30,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Burdock root? In curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.69,0:00:34.86,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Like daikon radish, it's a root vegetable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:36.66,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's got good texture and tastes good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:38.43,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.69,0:00:42.81,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Chicken, beef, seafood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:45.69,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Enoki mushrooms and spinach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:51.98,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, plenty of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:53.69,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it'd give you heartburn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:04.96,Susumu,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Masuoka Susumu (38)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:04.96,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's right. I'm absolutely certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:07.50,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,I did it for Erina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:10.54,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,No, Shohei-san did nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:14.54,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Please calm down. Tell us what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.54,0:01:16.63,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:20.08,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-kun, when did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:23.23,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever there's a case, \NMori Kogoro is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.23,0:01:27.27,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Inspector, what do \Nyou like to put in your curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.53,0:01:31.02,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-kun, is this really the \Ntime to be asking that question?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.56,0:01:36.15,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A journey of a thousand miles \Nstarts with the first step!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:38.48,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Solve 1,000 mysteries and enter a new world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:40.17,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A man protects his beloved wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.17,0:01:42.16,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What is the secret ingredient \Nthat changes the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.36,0:01:44.12,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Always determining the one truth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:45.50,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,with the body of a child \Nand the mind of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:48.58,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,his name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:35.98,DCEpTitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(396,1)}The Man Who Loved Too Much
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:32.83,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,"The Man Who Loved Too Much!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.23,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's review what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:42.74,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,This afternoon you went to the department \Nstore to buy a birthday present for Erina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:47.99,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,When you returned, you noticed that \Nthe window by the entrance was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:53.01,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You quietly entered the house \Nand looked in the living room,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:51.04,Shohei,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,460)}Sakuragawa Shohei (30) \NErina's Husband
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:56.18,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,where you saw the dead \Nman ransacking the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:57.54,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,A burglar, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:07.68,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The man noticed you, raised his \Nknife, and came towards Erina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.18,Erina,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Sakuragawa Erina (28)\N Housewife
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:13.69,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,However, Shohei-san fought back using a \Ngolf club that was in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:18.82,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,When the burglar fell, he hit his \Nhead on that object and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:22.79,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right... It... It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:26.45,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,But Shohei-san was preoccupied \Nwith protecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:32.36,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,We identified the dead man \Nby checking his phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:34.83,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Masuoka Susumu, 38 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:39.21,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,He previously committed forcible \Nentry and theft on three occasions,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:40.53,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,and had a criminal record.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:42.46,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,So he had previous offenses, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:45.84,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did that bag \Nbelong to the dead man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:52.60,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That jewelry is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:56.09,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,That matches their statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:05:01.23,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. This is a tragedy that occurred when \Na husband tried to protect his beloved wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:03.24,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:08.12,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you're honest when you testify \Nto the police or at the courthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:13.39,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they recognize Shohei-san's \Npure and noble love for Erina-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:15.50,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:18.93,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,And then repent for your crimes accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:20.55,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:24.63,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you won't have to \Ndo any sleeping this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:27.01,DCMain,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:30.22,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But there are a few other \Nthings I'd like to confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:31.19,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, kid. We've got shopping to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.11,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'd like to speak with you a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.11,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:37.90,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Tomatoes, avocados.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.55,0:05:41.33,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go all the way \Nand make goya champuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:45.11,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about champuru,\Nbut goya curry sounds pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:52.41,DCItalic,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:54.55,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A birthday card?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:56.16,Card,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Keep on being a beautiful lady \NShohei
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.03,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What's this doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:07.07,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:09.95,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to use their bathroom. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:11.93,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:26.19,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one pair of shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:29.53,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The golf bag is back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.10,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:34.70,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Erina and I entered through this entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:42.25,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,No, he entered through the back \Ndoor alone and grabbed a golf club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:44.88,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:47.75,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I was hoping to use your bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:48.84,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:50.13,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.32,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Erina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.42,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:11.70,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That shelf behind you is \Nfull of photos of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:16.20,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,My husband takes pictures of me practically \Nevery day and puts them on display.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:19.48,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Shohei-san must really love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:20.58,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:25.89,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,He tells me he loves me every day \Nand is completely devoted to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:30.37,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I've never \Ntold him that I love him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:33.22,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,he loves me more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:35.96,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:37.89,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-san, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.35,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.48,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,That's my precious collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:47.98,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,They're all European.\NThey're valuable and expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:53.61,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. But it's a good thing none of \Nyour photos or teacups were broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:56.08,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Lucky us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:08:00.25,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-san, could I speak with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:01.00,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:08.38,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of the house was \Nthoroughly ransacked,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.74,0:08:11.30,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,but their valuables are undamaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.37,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:21.91,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Just this spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:26.91,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That chair was knocked over, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:31.98,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Was the culprit sitting in this chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:35.66,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But why would a burglar sit in a chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:39.41,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:42.41,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Only that section of the \Nwall is a different color.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:45.42,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Was the calendar moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:47.54,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What's this doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:51.46,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What's this dent?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:55.47,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Was this calendar moved to hide this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:30.50,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,This was no ordinary burglary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:32.79,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,They lied about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:35.01,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Something must have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:50.00,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:52.89,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you were taking too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:55.22,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be wandering around back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:56.70,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:10:01.21,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-kun, you're still \Nhere? I thought you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:04.99,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. We'll be leaving right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:06.58,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:08.70,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:11.55,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Let go, Mister. They've got curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:12.50,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:14.59,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:17.09,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I detect the delicious smell of curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:21.53,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,That smells great. Is that tonight's dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:22.10,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:24.85,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,We're making curry today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.13,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,You two are going to cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:27.84,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:32.61,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Normally Ran handles all the cooking, \Nso we thought we'd surprise her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:36.36,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,We've been thinking about how \Nwe can make a tasty curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:39.28,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any secrets \Nto making a tasty curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:42.74,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, I'd appreciate \Nit if you could tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.49,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:47.35,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you tell them, Erina?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:47.87,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:50.87,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,About your secret ingredient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:52.63,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Secret ingredient?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:56.32,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,My Erina's curry is always \Nexceptionally good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:58.26,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Not even I know what the \Nsecret ingredient is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:11:02.26,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good, I could eat it every \Nday and never get sick of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:03.76,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Erina?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.76,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:08.25,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What's the secret ingredient?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:11.01,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:15.54,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, the secret ingredient \NI put in my curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:19.51,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,...is love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:27.14,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,I think about my beloved \Nhusband while I cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:33.17,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Erina-san. Can I try that curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:33.98,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:40.42,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry. I'm not confident \Nin my cooking today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.57,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid. Show some restraint.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:46.93,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Er, sorry about that. Truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:49.98,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What did they burn?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.56,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:01.91,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:04.62,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:07.26,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.87,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,There's something written on this notepad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:13.38,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:17.84,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,"I love you. I truly love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:19.25,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:22.38,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.92,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:26.64,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Go ahead and read the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.30,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:32.27,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,"So let's go to Lake Yamanaka today."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:36.94,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,I planned on taking her there \Nas a birthday surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:39.79,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,But I was too embarrassed\Nto tell her directly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:42.28,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd been practicing\Nby writing it on that paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:45.78,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Lake Yamanaka is a famous tourist spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:50.79,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But, Shohei-san, don't you tell Erina-san \Nthat you love her every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:53.54,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see why you'd need to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:58.52,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,No, Shohei-san wrote this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:02.55,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Shohei-san is the only person who \Nwould write that he loves Erina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:02.55,Notepad,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,I love you. I truly love you, \Nso let's go to Lake Yamanaka today. \NKeep on being a beautiful lady \NShohei
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:08.61,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,No, this isn't Shohei-san's handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:11.43,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean Masuoka wrote this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:16.34,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Was it Erina-san who was sitting \Nacross from Masuoka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:17.94,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but they were alone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.18,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I love you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:28.45,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit died when he hit \Nhis head on that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:30.27,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,So, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:32.83,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a boat weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.90,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,A boat weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:37.46,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, look. It says 3 kilograms on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:42.53,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Shohei-san and Erina-san, why \Nis this in your living room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:45.09,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Because I—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:46.89,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You bought it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:49.85,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you must have a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:53.22,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was thinking about buying a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.32,0:13:57.48,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,These are rope fibers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:03.61,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Could the culprit have brought this here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:07.99,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,What? The culprit brought it? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.25,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:16.04,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Shohei-san, I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:22.31,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,but could you and Erina-san come down to the \Nstation and tell us more about the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:25.43,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, you need to take your medicine first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.43,0:14:26.10,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,My medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:28.51,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You need to take it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:33.23,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,He has a chronic disease.\NHis medicine is in the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:34.59,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:44.65,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,You nearly told them the truth, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:47.03,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.53,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:52.16,DCMain,SHOEHI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:58.94,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. I'd do anything for you, Erina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:01.29,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,I love you. I love you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:05.80,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,I hate this about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:09.67,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you'd disappear and leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:12.18,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I asked him to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:15.82,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Asked him to do that? Disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:18.06,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:18.99,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:22.60,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,There you are. We're getting out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:23.69,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,We're going shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:27.61,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, sorry for staying so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:31.23,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you brat! You'd better \Nwait for me in the entryway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:35.08,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us. We should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:37.15,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.35,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.02,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:49.62,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:51.69,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:55.16,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:56.72,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Mori-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:16:00.35,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be leaving after I solve this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:01.88,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:04.52,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,It's already clear what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:08.36,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Shohei-san acted in self-defense \Nwhile protecting Erina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:09.67,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Self-defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:13.23,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:18.54,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,But Shohei-san and Erina-san \Nlied about the entire case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:21.87,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The two of them are fooling us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:24.43,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,They lied?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:27.38,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,They're fooling us? \NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:29.38,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I found something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:34.88,Card2,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Keep on being a beautiful lady \NShohei
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:30.75,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,On my way here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:34.88,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I found a birthday card for \NErina-san by the entryway,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:39.64,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,as well as Shohei-san's footprints \Nleading to the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:45.52,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Shohei-san, you left alone and \Nreturned alone through the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:49.52,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You've got mud from around the back \Ndoor on the hem of your pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:56.91,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Alone? Where was Erina-san then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:17:00.04,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,She was meeting with \NMasuoka inside this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:05.21,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,With Masuoka? Hold on, why \Nwould she be meeting him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:08.21,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Because Masuoka wasn't a burglar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:10.21,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,What? Who was he, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:11.79,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:17.22,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Masuoka probably told Erina-san \Nto invite Shohei-san on a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:19.90,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,At their destination,\Nhe'd kill him using a knife,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:23.40,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,use ropes to tie a weight to him, \Nand submerge him in the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.71,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,But Erina-san had a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:29.98,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't know how to invite \NShohei-san on a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:32.81,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she'd never \Ntold him she loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:36.49,DCItalic,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,I've never told him that I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:40.95,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Masuoka had Erina-san \Npractice by writing a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:43.50,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,That was the note we found.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:47.50,Notepad2,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,I love you. I truly love you, \Nso let's go to Lake Yamanaka today. \NKeep on being a beautiful lady \NShohei
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:47.50,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,"I love you. I truly love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.95,0:17:49.97,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,That's when tragedy struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:52.50,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Shohei-san came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:55.01,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,He mistook their meeting for an affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:56.02,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,An affair?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:57.51,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was a misunderstanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:04.18,DCItalic,MASUOAK,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:06.43,DCItalic,MASUOAK,0000,0000,0000,,Pour your heart into your writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:08.57,DCItalic,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,Pour my heart into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:12.32,DCItalic,MASUOAK,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, ma'am. "I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:14.34,DCItalic,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:16.69,DCItalic,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,"I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:23.69,DCItalic,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Erina loves that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:43.97,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Then Shohei-san's rage was \Ndirected towards Erina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:47.09,DCItalic,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,You were cheating on me with this guy, Erina?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:49.64,DCItalic,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,But I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:51.66,DCItalic,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be true, Erina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:55.82,DCItalic,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,You're married to me, but \Nyou've been seeing that guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:04.48,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,There's a dent hidden beneath \Nthe calendar behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:06.45,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You can check it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:09.33,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-kun, hold on. I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:12.68,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Invite? Kill? Submerge?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:14.60,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:17.34,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,What did Erina-san ask Masuoka to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:20.44,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,While looking for Conan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:23.60,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I happened to overhear them \Nspeaking in the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.96,0:19:27.47,DCItalic,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you'd disappear and leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:29.98,DCItalic,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I asked him to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:32.48,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,"Asked him to do that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:35.48,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,"I wish you'd disappear"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:40.99,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-san asked Masuoka to kill Shohei-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:43.01,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Kill Shohei-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:44.91,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She put a hit on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:48.54,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! I didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:52.17,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Takagi, could you \Ncheck inside the curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:56.04,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:03.70,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-san, is this the secret ingredient \Nyou included for Shohei-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:10.04,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-san intended to use that money \Nto pay Masuoka for Shohei-san's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:13.31,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,She invited Masuoka here \Nwhile Shohei-san was out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:15.06,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:20.07,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,There's blood on those bills. \NIt's probably Masuoka's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:24.45,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,And if thoroughly examined, Erina-san's \Nfingerprints may turn up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:29.33,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,After Masuoka was killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:33.34,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,there was still a mountain of evidence \Nleft of the hit on Shohei-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:36.65,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-san couldn't fool Shohei-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:41.46,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,So she convinced him to lie instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:44.82,DCItalic,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Erina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:46.45,DCItalic,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:52.24,DCItalic,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,If the police find out that I tried \Nto have you killed, I'll be ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.24,0:20:54.48,DCItalic,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Erina, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:57.96,DCItalic,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,Fool them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:58.61,DCItalic,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:02.49,DCItalic,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,If you love me more than anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:07.67,DCItalic,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,Lie for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:13.49,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.49,0:21:15.62,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! It's not her fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:19.51,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:22.61,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault that I couldn't \Nbecome Erina's ideal husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:25.63,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Because I couldn't die for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:30.01,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Because I couldn't keep her secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.91,0:21:33.58,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Erina's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:37.48,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Erina?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:40.88,DCMain,SHOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,My Erina?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:48.03,DCMain,ERINA,0000,0000,0000,,You creep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.09,0:23:16.02,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,This tastes really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.02,0:23:18.08,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You're not such a bad cook when you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:20.96,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Right? The word impossible \Nis not in my dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:44.65,DCNote,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Detective Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.28,0:23:24.81,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The final secret ingredient \Nis a pinch of salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.81,0:23:25.95,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's salty now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.95,0:23:27.48,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then we'll add some sugar cubes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.48,0:23:28.45,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's too sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.45,0:23:29.50,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ponzu, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.50,0:23:30.97,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,How about yakiniku sauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:33.42,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,No, this calls for wasabi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:34.96,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,How about red peppers?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:36.97,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, you've got to add an egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.54,0:23:40.30,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Ran-neechan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:42.83,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but could you pick \Nsomething up on your way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.29,0:23:44.44,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Bring us something!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.94,0:24:08.96,DCEpPreview,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.36,0:23:52.28,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,The victim was shot while \Nsleeping on the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.48,0:23:54.92,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He was shot with that shotgun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.98,0:23:57.23,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bloodstain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.71,0:23:59.82,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,This must've splattered \Nhere when he was shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.82,0:24:04.69,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But since there's no blood on the curtains, \Nthat means they were open then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.50,0:24:08.96,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying one of us killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:14.97,DCNextEp,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,The Novelist Known as the Demon King
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:13.39,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode of Conan is "The \NNovelist Known as the Demon King!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.98,0:24:34.91,Hint,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Curtains
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.36,0:24:32.84,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.84,0:24:34.12,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Curtains!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.91,0:24:36.11,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And the final secret ingredient is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.91,0:24:39.91,Don'tMiss,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.11,0:24:37.00,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.00,0:24:38.68,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm curtain no dish can \Nput my curry in the shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.68,0:24:39.71,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That was actually pretty good.
